$BBOLD Matrices. $EBOLD Know how to add, subtract and multiply matrices.
For example, if
$BR
\[
A = \begin{bmatrix}1 & 2 \\ 3 & 4\end{bmatrix}
\quad {\rm {and}} \quad
B = \begin{bmatrix}2 & -1 \\ 1 & 2 \end{bmatrix},
\]
then
$BR
\[
AB - B^2  = 
\begin{bmatrix}a & b \\ c & d \end{bmatrix}
\]
where
$BR
\(a = \) \{ ans_rule(10) \} ,
EOT
ANS(num_cmp(1));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT)); 
$BR
\(b = \) \{ ans_rule(10) \} ,
EOT
ANS(num_cmp(7));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT)); 
$BR
\(c = \) \{ ans_rule(10) \} ,
EOT
ANS(num_cmp(6));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT)); 
$BR
\(d = \) \{ ans_rule(10) \} ,
EOT
ANS(num_cmp(2));


